I'm so excited but also nervous because it
is the first time ever to be in the GP Paddock

00:00:30.199 --> 00:00:35.620
to be honest and the KTM bike is fantastic,
the Team. I can't believe everything is happening.

00:00:35.620 --> 00:00:40.820
It is all a dream. To ride a KTM on the MotoGP
circuit is absolutely amazing.

00:00:40.820 --> 00:00:47.580
Beautiful day here in Jerez for the first
round of the 2010, Red Bull MotoGP Rookies

00:00:47.580 --> 00:00:50.680
Cup. And what an exciting race we have got
in store.

00:01:03.140 --> 00:01:07.280
Same Qualifying as last year and last year
I managed to put off two podiums.

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:13.049
My plan is to just maybe follow the group
and then like maybe like the last two laps

00:01:13.049 --> 00:01:18.450
try to get up to first and just to like hold
it.

00:01:18.450 --> 00:01:25.450
Always mistakes start. So tomorrow I will
good start.

