There are at least 10 guys battling for the lead now. Still 12 laps
to go. So they are now touching. Now touching

00:01:43.789 --> 00:01:47.619
and that is taking the first 3 of them ride.
That is taking the first three of them out

00:01:47.619 --> 00:01:52.329
of contention. Well that really is messing
each other up. Hiura takes the advantage and

00:01:52.329 --> 00:01:56.329
behind him comes Danny Kent. He is going to
pay dearly to Daniel Ruiz for that mistake.

00:01:56.329 --> 00:02:01.200
Out on the main street they are all on the
slipstream there. Who has got the metal to

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:07.060
get it together. To get himself in the position
for that last corner breaking maneuver into

00:02:07.060 --> 00:02:12.209
the hairpin. It looks to me as though Danny Kent
has just done it, he is out

00:02:12.209 --> 00:02:19.209
And down goes another rider and that is Vavrous the Czeck rider. He has lost
it out. It is Danny Kent that leads across

00:02:19.750 --> 00:02:25.040
the line from Hiura to win the first race
of the Rookies Cup season. Ruiz it is that

00:02:25.040 --> 00:02:28.510
is the third ahead of Binder, Gagne, Alt and
Antonelli.

00:02:28.510 --> 00:02:32.640
Yeah it was a real hard race. There was about
6 or 7 of us running up front.

00:02:32.640 --> 00:02:39.640
The race was pretty hard. The start was okay
but after mistakes and losing

00:02:39.879 --> 00:02:45.810
positions. And the people was in front of
me they were like breaking me. And I couldn't

00:02:45.810 --> 00:02:50.629
go forward.
It was a crazy race. I'm glad just I finished

00:02:50.629 --> 00:02:54.810
it. Some guys out there just didn't have brains.
It was just crazy.

00:02:54.810 --> 00:03:00.129
My race was shut off finished like 8th. I
mean I was looking at battling for first

00:03:00.129 --> 00:03:07.030
but then again people were just going totally
wild like T-boning each other and stuff. So

00:03:07.030 --> 00:03:14.030
then I finished at like 8th place. So I am
not happy.

