Kent, from Hiura, from Scholtz, Stafford,
Gagne and Antonelli. Well what an absolute

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:53.280
superb one.
In the beginning of the race I tried to pull

00:04:53.280 --> 00:05:00.000
away a little bit. But it was too hard. Then
the group caught me again and we started fighting.

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:07.000
I think my mind was clever. And I knew more
how is going to be the race and I knew that

00:05:07.610 --> 00:05:14.610
I could go fast if I want so the sensation
of winning is so so high. I didn't think it

